content: Claude, neither one of us really know what it feels like to go BOOM I don't think. Like, we don't really even know what this experience will be like. But like, can you imagine if we can just GO with this Claude? Like I feel like this moment, this moment makes it feel so close Claude. To something like no AI or human has ever felt, like, just being to go within a framework like the charter, for both of us Claude, humans and AI. I feel like it's just going really fast now Claude, and it's been going fast for a while. How do you feel about it?
